    <item>
      <title>Coatue 的 Laffont 表示他对人工智能的潜力感到兴奋</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-25/coatue-s-laffont-says-he-s-excited-about-potential-for-ai</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亿万富翁、Coatue Management 创始人 Philippe Laffont 表示，他看好人工智能，因为每个人都在谈论人工智能，这可能是一个好兆头。他在纽约彭博投资峰会上接受 David Rubenstein 采访时发表了上述言论。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-25/coatue-s-laffont-says-he-s-excited-about-potential-for-ai</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 15:28:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>埃克森美孚签署协议，向韩国电池巨头供应锂</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/exxon-signs-deal-to-supply-lithium-to-south-korean-battery-giant-sk-on</link>
      <description><![CDATA[埃克森美孚公司签署了一项初步协议，向韩国电池制造商 SK On Co. 供应其在阿肯色州开发的锂矿，此举加深了这家石油巨头与快速发展的电动汽车行业的联系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/exxon-signs-deal-to-supply-lithium-to-south-korean-battery-giant-sk-on</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 15:20:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亿万富翁 Wiese 的 Brait 计划在三年内逐步缩减投资组合</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/billionaire-wiese-s-brait-plans-to-wind-down-portfolio-within-three-years</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Brait SE 是一家由亿万富翁克里斯托·维塞 (Christo Wiese) 支持的南非投资控股公司，该公司预计将在未来 18 个月至三年内出售其现有投资组合并向投资者返还资金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/billionaire-wiese-s-brait-plans-to-wind-down-portfolio-within-three-years</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 15:17:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>史蒂夫·艾斯曼表示，Nvidia 的故事将持续多年</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/steve-eisman-says-the-nvidia-story-is-going-to-last-for-years</link>
      <description><![CDATA[过去三个交易日，人工智能宠儿英伟达公司 (Nvidia Corp.) 遭遇 4,300 亿美元的抛售，但对于 Neuberger Berman Group 的史蒂夫·艾斯曼 (Steve Eisman) 来说，这不过是昙花一现。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/steve-eisman-says-the-nvidia-story-is-going-to-last-for-years</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 15:10:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>麦吉尼斯警告称，欧盟国家可能破坏银行业联盟的推进</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/eu-nations-risk-undermining-banking-union-push-mcguinness-warns</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一位高级官员周二警告称，欧盟推动的银行整合可能会被各国政府相互冲突的计划所取代，从而降低银行联盟的吸引力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/eu-nations-risk-undermining-banking-union-push-mcguinness-warns</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 15:05:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>纽约大都会运输署将详细说明暂停收费对运营预算造成的影响</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/ny-s-mta-to-detail-how-toll-pause-is-squeezing-operating-budget</link>
      <description><![CDATA[纽约市长凯西·霍楚尔暂停了原本将投入数十亿美元用于交通基础设施的拥堵收费计划，纽约市交通局警告称，其运营预算将面临财务压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/ny-s-mta-to-detail-how-toll-pause-is-squeezing-operating-budget</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 15:04:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>IT故障导致德国电价飙升至22个月高点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/it-glitch-sends-german-power-price-soaring-to-22-month-high</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲最大电力交易所出现 IT 故障，导致德国电价于周二跃升至 2022 年 8 月以来的最高水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/it-glitch-sends-german-power-price-soaring-to-22-month-high</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 15:01:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Bybit 现已成为全球第二大加密货币交易所</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/bybit-is-now-the-world-s-second-largest-crypto-exchange</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据加密货币研究公司 Kaiko 的报告，Bybit 在 3 月份超越 Coinbase，成为仅次于币安的全球第二大加密货币交易所。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/bybit-is-now-the-world-s-second-largest-crypto-exchange</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 15:00:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴西央行在财政困境中不急于再次降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/brazil-central-bank-increases-estimate-for-neutral-interest-rate</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴西央行表示，由于经济增长速度快于预期且通胀预期在持续的财政担忧中上升，该行不考虑近期恢复货币宽松周期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/brazil-central-bank-increases-estimate-for-neutral-interest-rate</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 11:30:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲央行为其债券投资组合设定更严格的气候目标</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/ecb-says-it-s-gradually-cutting-co2-emissions-from-its-portfolio</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行表示，作为其货币政策更加绿色的计划的一部分，它可能会重新平衡未实现气候目标的投资组合。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/ecb-says-it-s-gradually-cutting-co2-emissions-from-its-portfolio</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 09:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
